tasks.name: Special Dispatch
tasks.desc: Forest of the Fallen - Divine Ruins - Braseria
tasks.acceptNpcWord:
As a quartermaster of Undead Army, I've got to distribute lots of military materials every day. Yet, few soldiers are available to order about. This work is a real headache for me. 
You look quite strong. Do an errand for me, will you? This box of Supply Crates is to be delivered to the wizards at Divine Ruins. Hurry up, or Wizard Braseria will complain again.

tasks.name: Learn To Improvise
tasks.acceptNpcWord: The portal is fixed, but the army is getting more, we are out of supply, the soldiers are straved, you are energic, please get some hunter dog's meat for them.

tasks.name: Troll's armour
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Those  rock devil's armour is rare, go get some pieces, we could learn some skills.

tasks.name: Dangerous assassin
tasks.acceptNpcWord: The burning assassins in western camp bring us too much damage, we need to revenge.

tasks.name: Defense the wizard
tasks.acceptNpcWord: According to the newest situation, the wizard in eastern camp is preparing to attack us, you should stop it.

tasks.name: secret treasure of pirate
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Recently, Demon Pirates are often seen nearby, they have the secret treasures. If you are brave enough, bring some back to me!

tasks.name: Captain's cigar
tasks.acceptNpcWord: My cigarbox was stolen by those senior sailors, it’s impossible to find them all, bring a box back!

tasks.name: Delicious crab
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Have you seen the burning crab? They looks horrible, but the pincers taste delicious. Believe or not? Bring some back!

tasks.name: Dragon's Blood
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Recently, Prison Dragon is often seen nearby, it’s an ancient living beings and can be used to drug, bring some back to me!

tasks.name: Lizards Meat
tasks.acceptNpcWord: We will run out of food soon, take some lizards meat back!

tasks.name: Target:Corrupted Lord
tasks.acceptNpcWord:
If you still want your reward you need doing this job stealthily. Kill Corrupted Lord of Ancient Arena. Do not let anyone aware.

heroes.name: Falk
heroes.desc: An imperial wizard of great acclaim in his past life, Falk has continued to serve the arcane arts in death.

heroes.name: Leonine
heroes.desc: A serious and kind Druid who believes firmly in the goodness of his people, he is known far and wide for his loyalty and devotion.

heroes.name: Adara
heroes.desc: A courageous ranger of the Eternal Forest, Adara is the founder of a legendary school of archery known amongst all elves. A member of the Twelve Sacred Guardians.

heroes.name: Kerr
heroes.desc: An adamant believer in the power of magic, he believes magic can solve all of the world's problems. His strong opinions and radical vision often surprise those around him, but no ones dares to confront this powerful mage.

heroes.name: Adara
heroes.desc: A courageous ranger of the Eternal Forest, Adara is the founder of a legendary school of archery known amongst all elves. A member of the Twelve Sacred Guardians.

heroes.name: Adara
heroes.desc: A courageous ranger of the Eternal Forest, Adara is the founder of a legendary school of archery known amongst all elves. A member of the Twelve Sacred Guardians.

heroes.name: Helmi
heroes.desc: Her rapid climb in the ranks of the Cavalry Division is attributed not merely to her outstanding horsemanship, but also to her sound understanding of strategy and tactics. She's never met a worthy opponent in the division's annual horseback archery contest.

heroes.name: Bonatice
heroes.desc: A priestess who, through rigorous training and study, has broken the bonds of space and time. She has the ability to time travel and alter the course of events both in the past and in the future.

heroes.name: Lobo
heroes.desc: An elven dryad who wields the power of nature at his fingertips. A senior member of the Twelve Sacred Guardians.

heroes.name: Abaddon
heroes.desc: A rare member of the elven race who has mastered the power of fire and flame. Unlike his brethren who take more to nature and life, Abaddon enjoys the smell of smoke and burning instead.

heroes.name: Caelen
heroes.desc: A priestess from the mysterious lands of the east, Caelen uses arcane magic to bolster the defences of her troops and heal the injured. She is also a member of the Twelve Sacred Guardians.

heroes.name: Bonatice
heroes.desc: A priestess who, through rigorous training and study, has broken the bonds of space and time. She has the ability to time travel and alter the course of events both in the past and in the future.

tasks.name: A Hidden Gem II
tasks.desc: Embed 2 gems into any of your items.
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} embed 2 gems into any of the items.
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Embedding gems into your equipment will increase the attributes of that equipment. Each gem gives its own attribute bonuses and you should put careful consideration into which gems to embed into which equipment.
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Embedding gems into your equipment is a great way of increasing that equipment's attributes. Try embedding a gem now.
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: Now that you've embedded a gem into your equipment, did you notice that its attribute stats have increased?

tasks.name: Learning Skills
tasks.desc: Teach a Skill to one of your heroes or upgrade an exisiting Skill.
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} taught a Skill to one of the heroes or upgraded an exisiting Skill.
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Apart from equipping your heroes with equipment, another way of increasing their attribute stats is to teach them skills.
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Teaching your hero skills is a good way of increasing their combat ability.
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: Your hero has learned a new skill, increasing his/her attribute stats.

tasks.name: Maximizing Your Troops
tasks.desc: Use a Troop Supply Card to maximize the number of recruitable units.
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} used a Troop Supply Card to maximize the number of recruitable units.
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Once you recruit units, the recruitment limit will recover over time. The recruitment limit for advanced units recovers more slowly. However, you can instantly maximize the recruitment limit by using a Troop Supply Card.
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Have you tried using a Troops Supply Card yet?
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: Troops Supply Cards come in handy when you need to replenish your army in a hurry.

tasks.name: Arena Battle II
tasks.desc: Challenge other players at the Ranked Game and win 2 times.
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} challenged other players at the Ranked Game and WON 2 times.
tasks.acceptNpcWord: The Arena allows you to fight against other players. Challenging another player will increase your Honor and if you win, your Arena Score and Ranking will also increase. Your task is to challenge some players in the Arena and obtain some victories.
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Have you challenged other players and won a few times yet?
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: Now that you've won a few battles, your Arena Score and Ranking have both increased.

tasks.name: Beat the Boss I
tasks.acceptNpcWord: The monsters that lurk in Dungeons are an ever-present danger to our people. The most dangerous monsters in Dungeons are Dungeon Guardians. You will also gain rare and useful items by defeating them.
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Have you defeated enough Dungeon Guardians yet?
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: Each Dungeon is guarded by three Dungeon Guardians.

tasks.name: Star Struck
tasks.desc: Use a Book of Astrology to refresh the heroes list at a Tavern.
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} used a Book of Astrology to refresh the heroes list at a Tavern.
tasks.acceptNpcWord: A Book of Astrology is a powerful item indeed. Use one at the Tavern and your'll almost certainly attract some very powerful heroes.
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Have you used a Book of Astrology yet?
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: Legendary heroes aren't born every day. I hope you had the fortune of meeting one.

tasks.name: Bounty Quest: Reptilian Underling
tasks.desc: Haunted Copse - Altar of the Demontree - Reptilian Underling (0/3)
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} killed Reptilian Underling in Altar of the Demontree.
tasks.acceptNpcWord:
My army strikes the Altar of the Demontree tonight. I hope someone will aid me and kill 3 Reptilian Underlings stationed at the entrance. 
——Appointed: (East Border Commander) Deron Aileon
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Current quests in progress are——Reward: Reptilian Underlings

tasks.name: Heart of fire dragon
tasks.acceptNpcWord: We need one more thing to strengthen the new relic, it's heart of fire dragon it's rare and powerful, please take care.
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: You've got the fire dragon's heart, unbelievable.

tasks.name: Guidelines of the flamen
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} killed Poison  and obtained {!ItemList} in Dragon plain.
tasks.acceptNpcWord: Damn! Not keel,but the divination essential materials. Fortunately, there are still a lot of poison dragon alive in the dargon plain. Take back 3 dragon keel!
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: You can see these prison dragon in the dragon plains . Beware of their poison
tasks.finishNpcFinishWord: Thank you  warrior, I will give you direction.

tasks.name: Finishing Move
tasks.desc: Use the "Finish" function to instantly upgrade a building or research.
tasks.feedDesc: {!CharacterName} used the "Finish" function to instantly upgrade a building or research.
tasks.acceptNpcWord: When upgrading your buildings or research, you can click on the "Finish" button to instantly complete it.
tasks.finishNpcUnfinishWord: Have you tried the "Finish" button yet？
